node.text:
Why you need a Crystal Case! 👇 

Our Crystal series case has been a customer and staff favorite for many years. The Crystal-clear finish allows you to show off the color of your phone while not giving up any protection or convenience. We made the new Crystal case to feel thin and light in your hand but put extra protection in all the right areas.

With 1.75mm of corner, 1.5mm of screen, and 2.5mm of camera protection, the Rokform Crystal case boasts up to 4x more protection than other lesser cases. The bottom line, this case is built just as much for extreme use and abuse as it is for everyday carry and can easily withstand a 6-foot drop.
#iphone13 #iphone13case #iphone13mount #newiphone #iphonecase #caseiphone #iphonecases
